{"tid":1476934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"816 又撳港紙又美金，，力量分散，無撚用","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:16:24.000Z","uid":189799,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dbec50cc4767cf66bd9b508362fb2785ce953017","tid":1476934,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:30:56.000Z","msg":"見到有人撳港紙，有人撳美元，有人撳其他外幣。<br />\n其實你地知唔知撳錢背後嘅影響。<br />\n一開始個活動係叫人撳港紙，銀行手頭無咁多港紙，就要call loan<br />\n之後有人話撳美元，因為可以令政府嘅外匯儲備減少，衝擊佢個制度<br />\n撳其他外幣我唔知有咩用，大家可以解答下<br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇<br />\n撳港紙同撳美元係兩個唔同玩法。點解唔集中用一個方法呢，宜家咁只會兩頭唔到岸。<br />\n銀行現金流得幾百億，但外匯儲備有幾千億，邊個容易D<br />\n一開始係叫人撳港紙，唔知點解無端端有其他人話撳美元，完全分散哂力量。喱次咪撚話各自爬山呀"},{"pid":"2c01cde4093411f8d3b87391654ec7cef42f8059","tid":1476934,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"agger 諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40748b2fc85ded7ad630c80c63daef110a1b2129","tid":1476934,"uid":224897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"唯有兩邊都拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b58d73618c814834a8c8f8b2e0d1096f5a621a","tid":1476934,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40748b2fc85ded7ad630c80c63daef110a1b2129","tid":1476934,"uid":224897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"唯有兩邊都拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"兩邊都拎咪分散力量囉。"},{"pid":"8bbdd93f10e92b766380e7353334e14c8471ba54","tid":1476934,"uid":224897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5b58d73618c814834a8c8f8b2e0d1096f5a621a","tid":1476934,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40748b2fc85ded7ad630c80c63daef110a1b2129","tid":1476934,"uid":224897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"唯有兩邊都拎<img src=\"/